<item>
  <title>Upcoming Workshop and Hackathon at iEMSs 2025</title>
  <link>https://DaMIfLL.github.io/news/2025-06-iemss-workshop.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 





<p>We are excited to announce that DaMIfLL will host a workshop and hackathon at the International Environmental Modelling and Software Society (iEMSs) 2025 conference.</p>
<p>The event will bring together researchers and practitioners to collaboratively tackle data interoperability challenges in landscape and land use modelling. Participants will work hands-on with datasets and tools in a hackathon format.</p>
<p>More details on registration and the programme will follow soon.</p>



 ]]></description>
  <category>workshop</category>
  <category>hackathon</category>
  <category>iEMSs</category>
  <category>upcoming</category>
  <guid>https://DaMIfLL.github.io/news/2025-06-iemss-workshop.html</guid>
  <pubDate>Sat, 31 May 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
</item>
<item>
  <title>DaMIfLL at the FAIRagro Community Summit</title>
  <link>https://DaMIfLL.github.io/news/2025-03-fairagro-summit.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 





<p>Working group members attended the FAIRagro community summit, joining researchers and data infrastructure specialists to discuss FAIR data principles in the agricultural and landscape sciences.</p>
<p>The event provided valuable opportunities to exchange ideas, identify common challenges, and explore potential collaborations between DaMIfLL and FAIRagro initiatives.</p>



 ]]></description>
