<item>
  <title>DaMIfLL Presents at IAT Kickoff Meeting</title>
  <link>https://DaMIfLL.github.io/news/2025-01-iat-kickoff.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 





<p>Members of the DaMIfLL working group attended and presented at the IAT kickoff meeting. The presentation introduced the DaMIfLL initiative, outlined our working group structure, and highlighted ongoing efforts to improve data management and interoperability in land use and landscape research.</p>
<p>We look forward to continued collaboration with the IAT community.</p>



 ]]></description>
  <category>presentation</category>
