<div style="text-align: center">
<p><span class="text-support">Support</span>: Empowering IAT researchers to manage research data and software over the full scientific life cycle</p>
<p><span class="text-integration">Integration</span>: Connecting data and methods across IAT research groups</p>
<p><span class="text-transfer">Transfer</span>: Closing the loop between science and practice</p>
<p><a href="services.qmd" class="btn-brand">Learn more about our services and how we can support you</a></p>
